title: Partial remains of missing Bay Area woman found in Amador County
dc:creator: Gregory Yee
description: The partial remains of Alexis Gabe, 24, were found in an area where her ex-boyfriend Marshall Jones had traveled after her disappearance in January.
content:encoded: The partial remains of Alexis Gabe, 24, were found in an area where her ex-boyfriend Marshall Jones had traveled after her disappearance in January.

media:content.media:description: OAKLEY, CA - FEBRUARY 6: Friends of Alexis Gabe are photographed during a vigil at city hall Sunday, Feb. 6, 2022, in Oakley, Calif. Gabe disappeared on January 26, 2022. (Aric Crabb/MediaNews Group/East Bay Times via Getty Images)
